Lii-tarn Chen, 2001, “Imperfection of Market Structure, Financial Evolution and Economics Growth---The Case of Taiwan,” 國科會計劃報告(NSC89-2415-H-001-054)，中研院經濟所。
Lii-tarn Chen, October 1999 “Credit Constraints, Myopia and Structure Change—A test for Permanent Income Hypothesis to Taiwan’s Consumption,” mimeograph, IEAS, Taipei Taiwan.
Lii-tarn Chen, December 1998 “An Alternative Approach to Explain the Volitility of Price-Dividend Ratio.” mimeograph, IEAS, Taipei Taiwan.
(6).研究報告(包括委託研究報告、田野報告、調查報告)
